synopses.synopsis: A private detective drama that spanned 14 years and underwent seven changes in the title role. Johnny Dollar was 'America's fabulous freelance insurance investigator,' the 'man with the action-packed expense account.' He was always ready to fly to far corners of the country for a cut of recovered goods. He had an analytical mind, a nose for trouble, and the brawn to take care of himself when the going got dirty.
